text: Quintet is a 1979 American science fiction movie directed by Robert Altman and stars Paul Newman, Vittorio Gassman, Fernando Rey, Bibi Andersson, Brigitte Fossey and David Langton. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1979 science fiction movies Category:American science fiction movies Category:Movies directed by Robert Altman Category:Post- apocalyptic movies Category:Dystopian movies Category:1970s English-language movies Category:20th Century Fox movies
